    Trading gas with the EU if there's no Brexit deal
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">How cross-border gas trading with the EU will be affected if there’s a no-deal Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

